---
tagline:
  content: "\"How do you know I'm mad?\" said Alice.<br>\"You must be,\" said the Cat, \"or you wouldn't have come here.\""
  cite: "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland"
---
<%- partial('_partial/cover', {
    path_to_cover: config.cover.path + config.cover.home,
    path_to_thumbnail: config.cover.thumbnailpath + config.cover.home,
    cover_position: get_cover_position(config.cover.home),
    thumbnail_base64: get_thumb_base64(config.cover.home)
  }, {
    cache: !config.relative_link
  })
%>

<%- partial('_partial/tagline') %>
<div class="home-main">
  <p>欢迎光临本博客！这里主要是记录 Web 前端相关的一些内容，偶尔涉及其它方面。</p>
  <p>可以点击下面查看分类，移动设备上右滑即可出现菜单：</p>
  <a class="home-entry-wrap js-progressive-bg-container" href="/categories" style="background:url(<%- config.cover.path + config.cover.categories %>) <%- get_cover_position(config.cover.categories) %>/cover">
    <div class="home-entry-bg-thumb js-progressive-bg-thumbnail" style="background: url('<%- get_thumb_base64(config.cover.categories) %>') <%- get_cover_position(config.cover.categories) %>/cover"></div>
    <h1 class="home-entry">Categories</h1>
  </a>
  <p>按标签查找也可以比较方便地找到相关内容：</p>
  <a class="home-entry-wrap js-progressive-bg-container" href="/tags" style="background:url(<%- config.cover.path + config.cover.tags %>) <%- get_cover_position(config.cover.tags) %>/cover">
    <div class="home-entry-bg-thumb js-progressive-bg-thumbnail" style="background: url('<%- get_thumb_base64(config.cover.categories) %>') <%- get_cover_position(config.cover.tags) %>/cover"></div>
    <h1 class="home-entry">Tags</h1>
  </a>
  <p>查看全部文章的存档：</p>
  <a class="home-entry-wrap js-progressive-bg-container" href="/archives" style="background:url(<%- config.cover.path + config.cover.archives %>) <%- get_cover_position(config.cover.archives) %>/cover">
    <div class="home-entry-bg-thumb js-progressive-bg-thumbnail" style="background: url('<%- get_thumb_base64(config.cover.categories) %>') <%- get_cover_position(config.cover.archives) %>/cover"></div>
    <h1 class="home-entry">Archives</h1>
  </a>
</div>

<%- partial('about') %>
